        "text_GHmX9c": {
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>As you can imagine, shipping beverages can be quite costly due to weight and we've done our best to absorb most of the costs. Depending on your Club BERO enrollment, we offer three shipping tiers:</li><li>Non-members: complimentary ground shipping with any purchase above £65 </li><li>Club BERO Free Members: complimentary ground shipping for any purchase above £50 </li><li>Club BERO BEROMASTERS: complimentary ground shipping on all orders with no minimum</li></ul><p>For orders under our complimentary shipping thresholds, we charge a £5 flat fee.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_LmHpPV": {
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You can expect your order to arrive within 2-3 business days. Orders of more than 24 beers will be shipped in split shipments. Please check the tracking information contained in your order notifications (email/SMS) for additional packages under the same tracking number.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_KbdkdY": {
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We do not accept returns for our beer because we cannot guarantee the quality of the liquid when the product travels back and forth. If you experience any issues or the beer does not meet your expectations, please reach out to <a href=\"mailto:support@bero.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">support@berobrewing.com</span></a>. We are committed to ensuring our consumers are happy and will work with you to find a solution.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_V3n8Nh": {
