          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>If you would like to change or cancel your order, please contact <a href=\"mailto:support@bero.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">support@berobrewing.com</span></a>. Be sure to change or cancel your order before it has shipped.</li><li>If you would like to cancel a gift card order, please contact <a href=\"mailto:support@berobrewing.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">support@berobrewing.com</span></a> order within 14 days of purchase or scheduled send to recipient (whichever is later). The gift card must be unused in order to cancel.</li></ul>"
